+        DESCRIPTION 
+           "Enables or disables IGMP snooping in the system.
+            When set to 'enabled', the IGS module forwards packets 
+            to report to all port.
+            When set to 'disabled', the IGS module forwards packets 
+            to router port only."
+        DEFVAL  { 2 } 
