+
+      snmpGlobalState OBJECT-TYPE
+           SYNTAX      INTEGER {
+                          enabled(1),
+                          disabled(2)
+                       }
+           MAX-ACCESS  read-write
+           STATUS      current
+           DESCRIPTION
+               "This object is for enabling or disabling SNMP Community function."
