+	}
+	
+	lldpXdot1ConfigPortVlanTxEnable OBJECT-TYPE
+	    SYNTAX      TruthValue
+	    MAX-ACCESS  read-write
+	    STATUS      current
+	    DESCRIPTION
+	            "The lldpXdot1ConfigPortVlanTxEnable, which is defined as
+	            a truth value and configured by the network management,
