+        mstCistBridgePriority OBJECT-TYPE
+           SYNTAX      Integer32 (0..61440) 
+           MAX-ACCESS  read-write     
+           STATUS      current 
+           DESCRIPTION 
+              "The writable portion of the MSTI Bridge Identifier.
