+        
+    laPortChannelMode OBJECT-TYPE
+       SYNTAX       PortLaMode
+       MAX-ACCESS   read-write
+       STATUS       current
+       DESCRIPTION
+         "Current Operating Channel Mode of the port channel
+                     Lacp(1)    - forcing the port to negotiate with the
