+           STATUS      current 
+           DESCRIPTION 
+              "The value in the Type/Len field of a frame that will
+              be matched to trigger this filter. The default value of
+              this object is '-1', which means the rule don't care this 
+              condition."
+           DEFVAL  { -1 }
