+        
+        aclL2RuleSrcMacAddr OBJECT-TYPE 
+           SYNTAX      MacAddress
+           MAX-ACCESS  read-write 
+           STATUS      current 
+           DESCRIPTION 
+              "Source MAC address to be matched with the packet. By Default, the Source 
+               Mac Address will be zero, which means the rule don't care this condition..
+               address"
