+        aclL2RuleDstMacAddrMask OBJECT-TYPE 
+           SYNTAX      MacAddress
+           MAX-ACCESS  read-only 
+           STATUS      current 
+           DESCRIPTION 
+              "The MAC address Mask work for Destination MAC address.
