+           ::= { cpuFilterProfileEntry 15 }   
+
+        cpuFilterProfileOffset2Mask OBJECT-TYPE 
+           SYNTAX      OCTET STRING
+           MAX-ACCESS  read-write 
+           STATUS      current 
+           DESCRIPTION 
