+           ::= { cpuFilterProfileEntry 18 }   
+
+        cpuFilterProfileOffset5Mask OBJECT-TYPE 
+           SYNTAX      OCTET STRING
+           MAX-ACCESS  read-write 
+           STATUS      current 
+           DESCRIPTION 
+              "The CPUInterfaceFilter Profile Offset5 mask.
+               If Offset5 is turn on in cpuFilterProfileMask, 
