+	    SYNTAX      SEQUENCE OF LldpXdot3RemPortEntry
+	    MAX-ACCESS  not-accessible
+	    STATUS      current
+	    DESCRIPTION
+	            "This table contains Ethernet port information (as a part
+	            of the LLDP 802.3 organizational extension) of the remote
+	            system."
