+                DESCRIPTION
+                    "This object indicates the maximum number of router hops that the DHCPv6 packets can cross."
+            ::= { dhcpv6RelayControl 2 }
+
+            dhcpv6RelayEnablePortlist OBJECT-TYPE 
+               SYNTAX      PortList
