+                disabled(3)
+                }
+        ACCESS  read-only
+        STATUS  mandatory
+        DESCRIPTION
+            "Remote Insight/ Integrated Lights-Out Video Hardware Status.
+
+            The following values are defined:
+
+            other(1)
