+
+    cpqSm2CommBaudRate OBJECT-TYPE
+        SYNTAX  INTEGER
+        ACCESS  read-only
+        STATUS  mandatory
+        DESCRIPTION
+            "The baud rate to be used over this communication medium by the
+            Remote Insight."
